{"tid":1884951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子捱斬頭傷衝落樓求助 婆婆遭撞跌撼穿頭　","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T03:05:14.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15586b8c6ddf835000f41bb31aa3a267f37c2337","tid":1884951,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98vDNhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98vDNhf.jpg&h=d1eec284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員到場調查。翁鈺輝攝<br />\n<br />\n深水埗大南街203至205號一幢大廈，早上8時40分，一名年約40多歲男子，在樓上閣樓單位與人爭執，其間被人斬傷，頭部淌血，他負傷走落樓求救，其間一名老婦行經，遭男事主撞跌撼穿頭流血，一名男子在樓上取了一卷抹手紙，為兩人揩血，救護員接報到場，將男事主及婆婆一併送院治理，警方封鎖現場調查，稍後帶走一名男子返署助查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200218/SO3JVFZZUESHYBPQNUKZOZZCG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200218%2FSO3JVFZZUESHYBPQNUKZOZZCG4%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=8fb86ca7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200218%2FSO3JVFZZUESHYBPQNUKZOZZCG4%2F&h=93679798\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200218/SO3JVFZZUESHYBPQNUKZOZZCG4/</a>"},{"pid":"39be5f55ca4f17cb13206cfd5433d19066004732","tid":1884951,"uid":251945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"嗰阿婆好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9df30b90d764d211be97b02f12a7a3a048df36","tid":1884951,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:05:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/01/20190106/20190106_103834_059.html?type=ticker\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019%2F01%2F20190106%2F20190106_103834_059.html%3Ftype%3Dticker&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=121100f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h